	   <tr><td colspan=2>Without a doubt this is one of the best robes going.&nbsp;&nbsp;I like to compare it to a dreamweaver robe that has i believe sta12 int14 mana40 and a few array of resists.  However, the Loam robe in my opinion is far nicer.  80mana is equivalent to about 17 or 18 int, combine that with the 5 int it comes with and you have a nice 22 int robe.  Dreamweaver robe is equivalent to about 23 or 24 int robe but its gawd awful yellow and no drop.  There are usually less than 5 Loam robes  on each server due to their rareness, which in my opinion, makes them even more coveted and valuable.  The robe looks &quot;prestigious&quot; when worn and i was lucky enough to come across a level 59 chanter that sold it to me for 6k, far less than its worth.  He needed the money to buy KEI.  And when a better robe becomes available i can resell this one because wonderfully it is not no drop.    <br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Sat Oct 19 16:32:50 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
